DISCLAIMER:

This software is provided as an AI-powered assistant for detecting potential
job scams. It is not infallible and should not be used as the sole method for
determining whether a job posting is legitimate or fraudulent.

Users should:
- Always verify job postings independently
- Never share sensitive personal or financial information without verification
- Report suspected scams to appropriate authorities
- Exercise common sense and caution

The authors and contributors of this software:
- Make no guarantees about the accuracy of predictions
- Are not liable for any losses or damages resulting from use of this software
- Do not guarantee that all scams will be detected
- Are not responsible for false positives or false negatives

Use at your own risk.
